# Notion Project Workflow

This is a local + Notion dual-track project.

## Start Every Session

1. Read `AGENTS.md`
2. Read `docs/ai-context.md`
3. Read `docs/HANDOFF.md`
4. Read `docs/notion-sync-policy.md`
5. Read `manifest.yaml` and `NOTION_INDEX.md`
6. Unless privacy is `private-local`, read `docs/suggested-assets.md`

## Rules

- Structure changes: update local docs and manifest before Notion
- Task status: Notion is authoritative; mirror to CSV
- Never store Notion URLs only in chat; write them to manifest and NOTION_INDEX
- Append `CHANGELOG.md` after maintenance sessions
- For long-running work, provide a plan before changing local files or Notion resources
- After substantial work, update `docs/ai-context.md` Current State and Last Session
- At milestones or project pause/end, run ide-toolbox `session-handoff.sh`
- Promote only sanitized reusable patterns to `05_Agent-Library`; never promote private-local content
